text: Anne-Laure Florentin (born 9 November 1991) is a French karateka. She is a three-time European champion in the women's kumite +68 kg event. == Career == In 2017, she won the bronze medal in the women's kumite +68 kg event at the 2017 World Games in Wrocław, Poland. In 2016 and 2017 she won the gold medal in the women's kumite +68 kg event at the European Karate Championships.
